metadata.name: Laya
metadata.description:
Laya is the first phase of my life.
She was music that moulded me,
Untouched by emotions,
Pure and naive,
Oblivious of what's coming,
Brimming with innocence, she enters,
The glorious world of chaos they say,
Her melodies murmuring in my ears,
Guides me as I begin my trail,
To find peace within and
Beauty in chaos.
